From the get-go, it was clear that a productive relationship between Amazon=
 and the
stewards of the billions-grossing James Bond franchise was not possible. An=
d now, after years of failing to manage their talent, Jeff Bezos and Mike H=
opkins have simply thrown more money at the problem.

Matthew Belloni ( https://puck.news/author/matthew-belloni/?utm_campaign=3D=
