prio to star in <strong>Damien Chazelle</strong>=E2=80=99s next movie, the =
long-gestating <strong>Evel Knievel</strong> biopic centering on his famous=
 Snake River jump. Scorsese, by coincidence, was at one point attached to d=
irect that project, based on a<strong> William Monahan</strong>
